<title>良心推荐：看完这5部BBC神级纪录片，英语水平提升几个Level！</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/p4voAJSPkv</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/p4voAJSPkv</guid>
<description>&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;第一次见到雪梨，是在一次全国口语演讲比赛上，当时我的身份是选手，她是志愿者。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf0BRcCo0lkm1teZraPjs4yicw6yeoWPQMfiaGVngNT1H4agMBNlxNutCspH5wz16ReK2rfbXSmD7Ugg/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;95.57522123893806&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;628.6725663716815&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;23.36283185840708&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;412.03539823008856&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7298311444652908&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;533&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf0BRcCo0lkm1teZraPjs4yic11zVUBUenZcfNnbsW8E4PZmzhPSHI5fiaoiaevbphseM6oIl0NEfsdOQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;那次比赛，我得了冠军。她像个小迷妹，跑来跟我搭讪说：“要沾沾仙气，万一有一天突然开窍，英语像我一样好呢！”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;后来，我们成为了朋友，我才愕然发现，&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;英语专业的她，英语却差得令人发指。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;我也从未见过，有像她那般，对英语厌恶至极的人。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;问及原因，她说：“英语折磨了我十年，我根本看不到任何希望。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;“我每天花8个小时背单词、记语法、上培训班，通通都没用……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;可笑的是，高考因为英语太差，我第一志愿被淘汰，竟还被迫调剂到了英语专业……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;平日活泼开朗的她，强忍着眼泪说：“在大学里吊了2个月车尾，我跟父母摊牌要退学。却被连夜乘火车赶来的父母打了一巴掌。没人能理解我的痛苦。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6671875&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf3l8kS1exmy7K2oyF1gicooia5PNibIoKqdZ5X0jmV6eMf9Eaf2V54jy8RX0ia6owTUJRjttxxGczzUuw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;当下，我决定帮她一把。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;在花了近3个小时，了解到了雪梨的学习经历后。我做的第一件事，就是让她&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;扔掉单词书、语法本&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;。接着，我重新为她制定了学习计划，并&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;要求她每天学英语不要超过30分钟。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;她很诧异，但在我一再要求下，还是将信将疑地，按照我给的计划开始学习……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;span&gt;3个月后，我收到了雪梨发来的消息，她那学期的专业成绩拿了第一。从此，便一发不可收拾：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&quot;&quot; data-type=&quot;2&quot; data-url=&quot;&quot; data-author-name=&quot;&quot; data-content-utf8-length=&quot;57&quot; data-source-title=&quot;&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; readability=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;半年刷爆各种英语考试证书；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;大学毕业前，成功申请香港中文大学翻译专业研究生；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;还未毕业，提前拿到了新东方的offer。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;就这样，她顺着正确的道路，快速猛跑，后来，更是跑成了新东方精英英语教学主管。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;至此，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;她的人生轨迹，彻底发生了变化。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/edAXWNwKhU9Wc4gfCibpMKYMMA9HtN5NWibibianDUXia3icz3SILqPhNlkMM67sJKsQZEkdfw0hhdiaQC8tK9109KPtQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;从那时起，我就认为有必要跟大家分享一下：在英语学习中，最行之有效的方法——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;深析法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;10多年的教学经历告诉我：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;英语其实真没那么难！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;联合国教科文组织早就公布过，英语是全世界最容易学的语言，比中文还要简单好几倍！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;就像雪梨一样，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;英语之所以没学好，不是你不努力，而是你的方法错了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;01&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;英语有多简单？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;为什么中国人的英语世界倒数？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;大家好，我是Lotus。10多年来，我的学员们一直叫我Lotus老师。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6620370370370371&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; height=&quot;456&quot; width=&quot;690&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/edAXWNwKhU9Wc4gfCibpMKYMMA9HtN5NWx9sMwTDrx6ALdofxY3hWqk2NmiaEIBLLic7NYAku1wA1TpWRPiaiaxrX9g/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;剑桥大学专业认证培训师&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;美国EC  language school 优秀教师&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;NSEC口语测评大赛冠军&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.649074074074074&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/edAXWNwKhUibQkJTeIg8yBgmNIMcGnXra5saAydV62t6RVgVySc9L0PVaLuO0qhoE2JTcpKiaLhCu7z9nc2OF5Wg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&quot;&quot; data-type=&quot;2&quot; data-url=&quot;&quot; data-author-name=&quot;&quot; data-content-utf8-length=&quot;205&quot; data-source-title=&quot;&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; readability=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;10&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;一位毕业不久的大学生，英语成绩虽然不错，但发音、交流却十分糟糕。在Lotus的指导下，不到2个月，就练就了标准的发音技巧。现在已经是一位时薪500，小有名气的雅思口语老师。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/edAXWNwKhU8YpDCia44S83XQ1uib2duBmgyzfSflN5aEYmtODc6kO0icNL9c4A5fH2sBQz3ukia06wm0Wib5NAZFia7g/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;1080&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;102.69413629160063&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;1160.4437400950872&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9796296296296296&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/edAXWNwKhU8YpDCia44S83XQ1uib2duBmg0myjRFnTMiaB4TgC0hO7MpicJ2ibcics3ZakQw4iaRyor3F5kxsmicBhL1aA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;一位58多岁的法国阿姨，因家庭原因要移民美国，从未说过英语的她，跟着Lotus学了5个月，日常交流无压力。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/edAXWNwKhUib0uwYvaqHfDuZWDdqhbWJJpfN8QicucyOCtBCpOjjqrzsNQLx7qMU9YPFgsFImasc8llR2kowEJkA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;410&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;76&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;416&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8292682926829268&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;410&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/edAXWNwKhUib0uwYvaqHfDuZWDdqhbWJJvsjvpicXfNfkc20suP4bHD7Frxcbvv7icgu6u7HtLZrhNM5b7rNW3xWw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lotus的好朋友雪梨，大一时因为英语差险退学，在Lotus的指导下，3个月成功刷爆各种证书，后来，更被新东方聘用成为教学主管。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;……&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;我在美国时，曾在国际著名语言学校EC language school任教。每年会接触来自中国、印度、法国、泰国、日本……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;近120个国家&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;、至少&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;25000名&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;前来学习英语的学生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;644&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;305&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.503125&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf0GTINp3f8L6icg0K8HwcqtDYj2Wef2ic6h169oqvQxPFFNUtK46JVRpAPA8XDLbKTj8WsLNf91jBKg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;我发现，我们中国学生就算是在国外沉浸式的大环境下，也经常表示：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;span&gt;英语太难了，我根本学不会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;可当他们从我这里顺利“毕业”，像雪梨一样，靠英语在职场、事业上突飞猛进之后，无不庆幸道——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;英语原来这么简单，还好没放弃&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;644&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;483&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf0GTINp3f8L6icg0K8HwcqtD5yRdL49FzPkbLKVPMEfVczosFwxZ0XQgyoSsnNh0pAjKu7wgcUyiaIQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;我用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;深析法&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;教出过身价千万的企业高管、出国深造的精英海归。甚至许多我曾教过的，已成为雅思、托福老师的学员都在用这个方式去教他们的学生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;回国后，我开始主要面向国内顶尖企业家，做私人英语培训师，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;私教课程费是6000元/时。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;可在英语教育领域待的时间越长，就越明显感到：中国人花费了10年，而真正能把英语用于沟通的还不到3%。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;644&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;414&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7490234375&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1024&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/PBZ3wOsyXf0GTINp3f8L6icg0K8HwcqtDPF2n8TkP5zpSGwj1xc1Q7F0bz3SbpKg8tUv2eBqicZ479sJEc2QKL8w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;劳而无功，为什么如此勤奋的中国人，学不好英语！？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

